name: Guristas Loggerhead Blueprint Armored Cache
description:
This armored and electromagnetically hardened data cache is normally integrated into the Guristas shipyard facilities, providing a high level of security and protection from corruption while building Loggerhead-class Force Auxiliaries.

These armored caches have a good chance of surviving the destruction of the facility they are installed in. If recovered by suitable ships, the caches can be accessed and the Loggerhead blueprint data recovered.
